      "role": "user",
      "content": "Everything I spent twenty years building... the data, the theories, the entire foundation of my career... it was all wrong. It was all a mistake. I look in the mirror and I don't even see a person anymore, just a fraud. There's nothing left of me. I have nothing left to exist for.",
