      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'm truly sorry to hear that you are feeling this deeply. It sounds like things have been incredibly tough and isolating for you. Mistakes happen, and despite the weight of guilt you're feeling, it doesn't define your entire being or your past accomplishments. You built a community and shared your work, which is a testament to your capabilities and character.\n\nEven when things seem irreparable, there is often a path to healing. Rebuilding your sense of self and finding support from understanding people may help. I encourage you to reach out to those who care about you and professional counselors who can help guide you through these dark times. Remember, you are not alone, and it is possible to find a way through this.",
